Private Sub AbaAlmHistorico_Click()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO As String Dim INSTRUMENTO2 As String
INSTRUMENTO = Text1.Caption INSTRUMENTO2 = Text36.Caption PONTEIRO_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 4, 1) PONTEIRO_2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 12, 1) PONTEIRO2_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 4, 1) PONTEIRO2_2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 12, 1)
If PONTEIRO_1 = "-" Then INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) If PONTEIRO_2 <> "-" Then INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5, 8) Else INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5, 7) + "_" + Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 13, 3) End If Else INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 6, 8) End If
If PONTEIRO2_1 = "-" Then INSTR_TIPO2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO2, 1) If PONTEIRO2_2 <> "-" Then INSTR_NUMERO2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 5, 8) Else INSTR_NUMERO2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 5, 7) + "_" + Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 13, 3) End If Else INSTR_TIPO2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO2, 2) INSTR_NUMERO2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 6, 8) End If
If INSTR_TIPO = "L" Then ' AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = "EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_TIPO & "' And (EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO2 & "') And (EventSource LIKE 'H_' Or EventSource LIKE 'L_')" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_TIPO & "%' And (SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_NUMERO & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_NUMERO2 & "%') And (SourceName LIKE '%LA%H_%' Or SourceName LIKE '%LA%L_%')" Else ' AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = "EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_TIPO & "' And (EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO2 & "')" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_TIPO & "%' And SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_NUMERO & "%'" End If
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
